1. Mi *želimo* da stvorimo uspešnu saradnju. (We wish to create a successful partnership.)
2. Oni *žele* da se vrate ponovo. (They want to come back again.)
3. *Želela* bih da vidim svoju porodicu. (I would like to see my family.)
4. Znamo da *želite* da postignete uspeh. (We know that you want to achieve success.)
5. On *želi* da se dobro zabavi. (He wants to have a good time.)